        <updateDate>2021-03-02T19:46:10Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Justice for Servicemembers Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill updates employment and reemployment rights of members of the uniformed services by making arbitration requirements unenforceable unless the parties consent to such arbitration in relation to employment or reemployment claims.</p>]]></text>
